      <scopecontent id="aspace_72b47c271dcbbd5f923a8828f04dc56b">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of drafts, notes, oral history interview tapes and transcripts, release forms, and other materials assembled by Richard D. Willits (Yale 1982) for his senior essay titled Out From Behind the Walls of Ivy: Dwight Hall and Student Activism in the 1930s and 1940s.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
